remarks.text: Bicycle conveyance

Berlin: Monday from 3 a.m. to 2 p.m. there may be restrictions (underground, bus). From Thursday, 3 a.m. to Friday, 3 p.m., underground trains, trams and most bus lines will not be running / Brandenburg: Wednesday strike in the Uckermark, Thursday in Ostprignitz-Ruppin, Friday in 8 districts and the independent cities. S-Bahn, regional and long-distance trains will be running. Information: www.vbb.de/streik and www.bvg.de
